<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
        h1 { color: #2a9d8f; font-size: 18px;} /* A nice green for "shipped" */
        .highlight { background-color: #e9f5f3; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.8em; text-align: center; color: #777; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Your Order is On Its Way!</h1>
        <p>Hi <%= order.customerName %>,</p>
        <p>Great news! Your Favorite Plug order (<strong>#<%= order.id.slice(-6) %></strong>) has been shipped and is now on its way to you.</p>
        
        <div class="highlight">
            <p><strong>Shipping To:</strong><br><%= order.shippingAddress %></p>
        </div>
        
        <p>You can expect your delivery soon. Thank you for your patience!</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for shopping with Favorite Plug!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>